messages.text: Remember the girl who has a crush on Ethan?
You remember her well, I'm sure of that
The one with beautifully long blonde hair :p
And also the one who seemed to has caught Ethan's heart
Well, if you did watch the news then you would've known, silly
Did she got hit by a truck?
You would love that wouldn't you?
Her parents found her dead in her room
Blood was all over the place
Are you for real right now, Hannah?
Who would want to kill her?
That's what I want to know
And it looks like the killer wants people to know that she got killed
What is going on with our town?
Last week, a kid was shot in the face
And now... someone from our school was killed
But honestly speaking, I don't think she has any enemies
She's kind of the school's sweetheart
Is it still on the news?
Ethan seemed affected by it, btw...
Yeah, like that's going to make me feel happy
I know that you like Ethan
But we can all tell that he has feelings for Summer
Wow, wth is wrong with you?
Summer's beautiful and she's a really nice person
Almost everyone in town was shocked to find out that she was killed
Maybe it's better for her to die
What do you even mean that she deserves it?
She was falling head over heels over my man
He is nobody's man ok. We both know that
He can like wheover he wants
You know that I like him
He has to like me back
I'm not trying to make you upset
But, there aren't any signs showing that he likes you...
Ethan's mine, I told her that
I know what you're going through
This has nothing to do with Summer
Ethan is likable, he's the quarterback, ffs
And fyi, he doesn't like you
He finds it ANNOYING and IRRITATING when you won't stop staring at him
I should have just killed you like how I killed Summer
Do you even realise what you're saying?!!!
I killed her so she won't be able to get Ethan
Like I said, Ethan is mine
And I trust you to not tell the police
